<div id="pf5d" class="pf w14 hd" data-page-no="5d"><div class="pc pc5d w14 hd"><img class="bi x0 y0 w15 he" alt="" src="bg5d.png"/><div class="t m4d8 x32 h19 y61b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 12 September 14-20 </div><div class="t m5cc x51 h45 yad3 ff5 fs1b fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">IE </div><div class="t m2f x9f h45 yad3 ff5 fs1b fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m6ec x5d h45 y87b ff5 fs1b fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ig 5cou</div><div class="t m83f x2c h45 yb53 ff5 fs1b fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m840 x27 h30 y39e ff1 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">n2 </div><div class="t m645 xd5 h46 y61d ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">AIT2 </div><div class="t m25c xee h47 yab9 ff3 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Urlit </div><div class="t m841 xbe h46 yab9 ff2 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">HEE3002t1 </div><div class="t m96 x1 h19 y446 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;I was given a sharp physical pain </div><div class="t m842 x0 h17 yb17 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rhich </div><div class="t m15e x6f h19 y447 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">came as Satan&apos;s messenger to </div><div class="t m843 x0 h19 y448 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ruise me; this was to save me from </div><div class="t mef x0 h19 y449 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eing unduly elated. Three times I </div><div class="t m42a x0 h19 y2e ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">egged the Lord to rid me of it, but his </div><div class="t ma5 x0 h19 y50e ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nswer was: &apos;My grace is all you need; </div><div class="t m12e x0 h19 yb54 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ower comes to its full strength in </div><div class="t m1ea x0 h19 y6f ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&apos;eakness&apos; &quot; (2 Cor. 12:7-9, NEB). </div><div class="t m5ee x1 h17 y44e ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;There are cases where God works </div><div class="t m6c8 x0 h17 y44f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ecidedly by His divine power in the </div><div class="t m56d x1 h17 y450 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">storation of health. But not all the </div><div class="t m116 x52 h17 y451 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ck are healed. Many are laid away to </div><div class="t m844 x52 h17 y30d ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eep in Jesus. John on the Isle of </div><div class="t m845 x0 h17 y453 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">atmos was bidden to write: &apos;Blessed </div><div class="t m66c x0 h17 yb55 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">re the dead which die in the Lord </div><div class="t m808 x52 h17 y454 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">om henceforth: Yea, saith the Spirit, </div><div class="t m846 x0 h17 y311 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">iat they may rest from their labors; </div><div class="t m847 x0 h17 yb56 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nd their works do follow them. </div><div class="t m1a9 x0 h17 yb1f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">evelation 14:13. From this we see that </div><div class="t m121 x52 h17 y455 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">persons are not raised to health, they </div><div class="t m848 x0 h17 y515 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hould not on this account be judged </div><div class="t m61b x0 h17 y457 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">s wanting in faith.&quot;—The </div><div class="t m849 x87 h17 y457 ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ministry of </div><div class="t m84a xee h17 y458 ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">!ealing, </div><div class="t m106 xeb h17 y458 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 230. </div><div class="t m84b x1 h17 y459 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Job&apos;s experience is an eloquent </div><div class="t m60a x0 h17 y45a ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">xample of unanswered prayer. He </div><div class="t m7b0 x0 h17 y45b ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ried &quot;Why won&apos;t God give me what I  </div><div class="t m84c x27 h17 yb57 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ask? Why won&apos;t he answer my prayer?&quot; </div><div class="t m26b x27 h17 y9c ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 6:8, TEV). And again, &quot;I call to </div><div class="t m568 x27 h17 y50d ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">you, 0 God, but you never answer; </div><div class="t m624 x27 h17 yb58 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and when I pray, you pay no attention&quot; </div><div class="t m476 x27 h17 y9f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 30:20, TEV). Job&apos;s problem was </div><div class="t m62e x27 h17 y520 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that he didn&apos;t have the information we </div><div class="t m84d x27 h17 y9d0 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">have in the first and second chapters </div><div class="t mb1 x27 h17 y521 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the book of Job. He was flying blind. </div><div class="t m84e x27 h17 y522 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He didn&apos;t know that every syllable of </div><div class="t m3b0 x27 h17 y9d2 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">his prayers was being heard by a loving </div><div class="t m289 x57 h17 y256 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God, and would eventually be </div><div class="t m84f x27 h17 y9d4 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">answered. </div><div class="t m850 x56 h17 ya7 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Bible is full of unanswered </div><div class="t m793 x27 h17 ya8 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prayers. &quot;Moses prays to enter the </div><div class="t m497 x27 h17 y527 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Promised Land, but dies on Nebo&apos;s </div><div class="t m564 x27 h17 y9d6 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">top, his request refused. In the midst </div><div class="t m851 x27 h17 y25b ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of national calamity the patriot lifts his </div><div class="t m3a6 x27 h17 y529 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lamentation, &apos;Thou hast covered </div><div class="t m852 x27 h17 yad ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thyself with a cloud, so that no prayer </div><div class="t m853 x27 h17 y52a ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">can pass through&apos; (Lam. 3:44); and the </div><div class="t m854 x57 h17 yb1 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prophet Habakkuk in his </div><div class="t m855 x27 h17 yb3 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">despondency exclaims, &apos;0 Jehovah, </div><div class="t m856 x27 h17 yb4f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">how long shall I cry, and thou wilt not </div><div class="t m297 x57 h17 yacd ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hear?&apos; (Hab. 1:2). Paul prays thrice that </div><div class="t m277 x27 h17 y52c ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a vexatious, physical handicap, a </div><div class="t m857 x57 h17 yb5 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&apos;thorn in the flesh, which hinders his </div><div class="t m858 x57 h17 yace ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">missionary labors, may be removed; </div><div class="t m859 x57 h17 y52e ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">but for the rest of his life he is </div><div class="t m7a3 x57 h17 yb9 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">compelled to make the best of it and </div><div class="t m85a x57 h17 y264 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">let it make the best of him (II Cor. </div><div class="t m85b x27 h17 y9d9 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">12:9). Even the Master in the Garden </div><div class="t m47f x57 h17 ybc ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prays for release from the appalling </div><div class="t m85c x57 h17 y9da ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cup, but goes out to drink it to the </div><div class="t m465 x57 h17 y268 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">dregs.&quot;—Harry Emerson Fosdick, </div><div class="t m4fe x12 h17 y268 ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The </div><div class="t m85d x27 h17 ybe ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Meaning of Prayer, </div><div class="t m85e x4b h17 ybe ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pp. 116, 117. </div><div class="t m29b x57 h19 yc2 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m63 x57 h19 yc5 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m724 x58 h19 yc5 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Universality of Death </div><div class="t m5de x58 h19 yc8 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Heb. 9:27) </div><div class="t m65 x57 h19 yb59 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m2d3 x58 h19 y283 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God Knows Best </div><div class="t m463 x58 h19 yb5a ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Isa. 55:8, 9) </div><div class="t m67 x57 h19 ycd ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m83d x58 h19 ycd ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Unexpected Ways </div><div class="t md9 x58 h19 yce ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Phil. 4:19) </div><div class="t m69 x57 h19 yb5b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t mf2 x58 h19 yb5b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Acting Rationally </div><div class="t m147 x58 h19 yd0 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(James 1:5) </div><div class="t m6b x57 h19 yb5c ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m579 x58 h19 yb5c ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Learning From Suffering </div><div class="t m72d x58 h19 yac6 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(2 Cor. 1:3, 4) </div><div class="t m6d x57 h19 y580 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m2d8 x58 h19 y580 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Persisting in Prayer </div><div class="t m5f7 x58 h19 ya4f ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rom. 12:12) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
